Class UserChoiceRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • propertytycoon.UserChoiceRequest

  • public class UserChoiceRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains the player options for the next step of the game. It is returned to the GUI after the Player has clicked the go button * to send the current selected option for processing.
